                and liability from its obligations and liabilities under clause 3.1, irrevocably
                and unconditionally agrees to indemnify the Creditor in full on demand against all
                losses, costs and expenses suffered or incurred by the Creditor arising from or
                in connection with from the failure by the Principal Debtor to make due and punctual
                payment of the Principal Debtor''s Obligations (or any part thereof) or resulting
                from any of the Principal Debtor''s Obligations being or becoming void, voidable,
                unenforceable or ineffective against the Principal Debtor.</p></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl>
            <dt>4 CREDITOR PROTECTIONS</dt>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify" >
