                being avoided, set aside or ordered to be refunded pursuant to any enactment or
                law relating to breach of duty by any person, bankruptcy, liquidation, administration,
                the protection of creditors or insolvency or for any other reason.</p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify" >
