                Guarantee against the Guarantor as if such release, discharge or settlement had
                not occurred and any such security, disposition or payment had not been made.</p></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl>
            <dt>8 PAYMENTS AND TAXES</dt>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify" >
