    </p></dd>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px;" >
        2.8 No amount repaid or prepaid may be redrawn under this Agreement.</p></dd>
</dl>
<dl>
    <dt style="margin-left: 30px;"><b>3. Security</b></dt>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px;" >
        3.1 The Customer''s obligations to the Creditor under this Agreement shall be secured
        by way
