            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px;" >
                (b) any expenses incurred by the Creditor in enforcing or preserving its rights
                under this Agreement and the Security with interest thereon at the rate applicable
                to the Loan, which may include expenses that the Creditor incur after as well as
                before any judgment or decree. These expenses will include (but not be limited to)
