        <dl>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px" >
                i. us ensuring that the information you gave us was not inaccurate or deficient
                in any respect (if we discover that it was, then the Agreement will be void and
                where appropriate may be reported to credit reference and fraud agencies);
            </p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px" >
                ii. us checking your credit reference and/or the information you provide to assess
                the affordability of the loan; and
            </p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px" >
                iii. where applicable, acceptance by us of the person you have nominated to act
                as Guarantor and provide a Guarantee, where applicable.
            </p></dd>
        </dl>
    </p></dd>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px" >
        6.2 You must accept the loan and sign the Agreement confirming acceptance of the
        Agreement and its associated Terms and Conditions before the acceptance deadline,
        which will be communicated to you at the time of your loan application</p></dd>
</dl>
<dl>
    <dt style="margin-left: 60px"><b>7. Preconditions</b></dt>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px" >
        7.1 The Creditor shall not be obliged to provide the Loan unless the following conditions
        are satisfied on the date on which the Loan is provided:-
        <dl>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px" >
