            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px" >
                (c) the availability as security for the Loan of any existing security is confirmed
                to the satisfaction of the Creditor; and</p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px" >
                (d) the Creditor is satisfied that no default event as outlined in Clause 10 (an
