        </dl>
    </p></dd>
</dl>
<dl>
    <dt style="margin-left: 60px"><b>8. Ending the Agreement and Early Repayment</b> </dt>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px;" >
        8.1 The Customer may end this Agreement at any time by repaying the full amount
        you owe under the Agreement at that time without premium or penalty.
    </p></dd>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px;" >
        8.2 You agree that we may demand repayment of the full amount owed by you under
        the Agreement if you:
        <dl>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px;" >
