            </p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px;" >
                (b) sell, transfer, lease or otherwise dispose of any assets (other than assets
                which are disposed of in the ordinary course of business);
            </p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px;" >
                (c) enter into any obligation, whether by way of borrowing from another source,
                leasing commitments, factoring of debts, granting of guarantees or by any other
