    </p></dd>
</dl>
<dl>
    <dt style="margin-left: 30px;"><b>10. Default</b></dt>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px;" >
        10.1 If any Event of Default occurs, then the Creditor may by written notice to
        the Customer declare the Loan, all interest accrued and all other sums payable by
        the Customer under this Agreement to be immediately due and payable and/or terminate
        the obligations of the Creditor under this Agreement.</p></dd>
    <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 60px;" >
        10.2 In the Event of Default, you will be liable for any fees costs and expenses,
