                the Customer to the Creditor proves inaccurate, false or intentionally misleading;
                or</p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px;" >
                (e) any resolution is passed, petition presented, proceedings commenced or other
                procedure or step taken in any jurisdiction for the liquidation of the Customer
                or any Subsidiary;</p></dd>
            <dd><p  style="text-align: justify; margin-left: 90px;" >
